    note right of TilingNonExplicitCompNonExplicit
        Initial state. Default mode is MODE_COPY_FROM_METADATA for both dimensions.
        setTilingMode(MODE_EXPLICIT) transitions to TilingExplicitUnsetCompNonExplicit.
        setCompressionMode(MODE_EXPLICIT) transitions to TilingNonExplicitCompExplicit.
        setTiling and getTile* methods are forbidden here.
        Compression detail methods require MODE_EXPLICIT and are forbidden here.
    end note

    note right of TilingExplicitUnsetCompNonExplicit
        Tiling is MODE_EXPLICIT but setTiling() has not been called yet.
        getTileWidth/Height/GridXOffset/GridYOffset throw IllegalStateException (params not set).
        setTilingMode with non-EXPLICIT value returns to TilingNonExplicitCompNonExplicit.
    end note

    note right of TilingExplicitSetCompNonExplicit
        Tiling is MODE_EXPLICIT and setTiling() has been called.
        getTileWidth/Height/GridXOffset/GridYOffset are available.
        setTilingMode with non-EXPLICIT value returns to TilingNonExplicitCompNonExplicit.
        Compression detail methods require MODE_EXPLICIT and are forbidden here.
    end note

    note right of TilingNonExplicitCompExplicit
        Compression is MODE_EXPLICIT but tiling mode is non-explicit.
        setCompressionType, getCompressionType, setCompressionQuality etc. are available.
        setCompressionMode with non-EXPLICIT value returns to TilingNonExplicitCompNonExplicit.
        Tiling detail methods are forbidden here.
    end note

    note right of TilingExplicitSetCompExplicit
        Both tiling (with params set) and compression are in MODE_EXPLICIT.
        All protocol methods are available.
    end note
